description:
Fyodor Patorichev was an http://anidb.net/ch1535 [Alliance] commodore. He served in the 13th Fleet under the command of Admiral http://anidb.net/ch737 [Yang Wenli]. He was with the fleet from the very beginning, participating in the capture of http://anidb.net/ch1762 [Iserlohn Fortress] in the Seventh Battle of Iserlohn.
Source: Gineipaedia
name: Fyodor Patorichev
